<br>
Unfortunately I did not do such a good job.  <br>
<br>
Naketh, I composed a couple responses to your post, but I couldn’t manage to get my point across without sounding too inflammatory.  I’d have loved to debate you on some of your points, but since ‘Henk’ is my character’s name, I’m a bit leery of tackling some of them.  I can just see phrasing something poorly and being tossed out of groups in Iceclad.  <br>
<br>
“Aren’t you the guy that said that MLK was the same as Hitler?”<br>
<br>
“No, no, that wasn’t my point, all I was saying was that…”<br>
<br>
“We don’t need your kind in our group, racist scum!”<br>
<br>
“Wait a minute, I…”<br>
<br>
You have been disbanded from the group.<br>
